      "date": "2013-07-04 21:45:34.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.4/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/04a88d8e-e4f0-11e2-9f63-52540035b04c).  Ran 14 tests.  No failures.",
