      },
      "date": "2013-07-18 17:19:37.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: I would prefer that you didn't submit this\n\nYes, OK. So, this patch is not needed.. Moving cfs_hash_create will be fixed if either one of these two patches land: http://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/5471/ or http://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/6843/\n\nThis patch should be abandoned.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "91c30f74e16d4772fc9f7be6ca9a808ee3029966",
      "author": {
